# Verticals + Topics (Not Apps)

## Model

```txt
Verticals  → public domain (books.foundryos.com)
Topics     → pages beneath vertical (1,961 registry entries)
```

**Never** create `{topic}.foundryos.com` subdomains.

## Public Sites

- `foundryos.com` — Mission Control (living HQ)
- `books.foundryos.com/fantasy` — topic page
- `bourbon.foundryos.com` — vertical home

## Required Packages

- `@foundry/seo-engine` — structured data, programmatic SEO
- `@foundry/knowledge-graph` — entities, relationships, internal links
- `@foundry/topic-registry` — 1,961 topic registry

## Before Building Niche UI

Ensure SEO engine, knowledge graph, topic registry, and pass tracking are in place.

## Pass Updates

Every pass updates: `docs/BUILD_LOG.md`, `docs/ROADMAP.md`, `docs/METRICS.md`, `apps/platform` build journal.
